com.paypal.selion.plugins

Enum TestPlatform

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<TestPlatform>
      • com.paypal.selion.plugins.TestPlatform
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<TestPlatform>

    public enum TestPlatform
extends Enum<TestPlatform>
    Represents the platform types code generation can be performed for. Also maps each platform type to a velocity template.
